item.title: Need help
item.dc:creator: @ziplock ziplock
item.description:
@ziplock wrote:

[quote=“Owner Spyder, post:7, topic:268271”]If you don’t know how to change that simple stuff, then i suggest you don’t run a server. You can learn but the TUT’s on here. If you want to make yourself owner go to “charters” section in your server and search for your name and look for “rights” and it should say “rights = 0” change to “rights = 3” .

P.S - Don’t put the " " 's.[/quote]

Or he can go to java.sun.com and learn java the legit way.

People need to study general java tutorials rather than tutorials relating to a specific java application; in this case a private server, but if you wanted to create a calculator in java I would not study a tutorial for that; I would study a tutorial on variables and usage with numbers in java.

Read full topic
